;;     blog, and make sure that it has the following lines:
;;     <!-- UPDATES HERE -->
;;     <!-- END OF BLOG HERE -->
;;
;; (5) in your .emacs put the following, replacing the ... with
;;     appropriate customizations.  Read the defvar statements below
